    <h2 class="heading--box-blue">Shape your pupils' futures</h2>
    <div class="inset">
      <p>Teaching maths opens the door for your pupils to pursue exciting careers. They could work in a diverse range of fields, from statistics and accountancy, to data science and programming.</p>
      <p>By solving challenging problems, your pupils could make significant contributions to these impactful areas.</p>
      <p>Your pupils will learn more from you than you might think. As their teacher, youâ€™ll guide your pupils though the skills they need to show their understanding of maths. You'll teach them valuable life skills such as critical thinking, decision making and problem solving.</p>
    </div>
   </section>

    <section class="col col-720">
   <%= render 'content/shared/quotes/quote_maths_dimitra' %>
